message.body: Hey Juila! I told you how tall that horse is right? 16hh still growing. Would you want to go meet him at all sometime? I'm free this week!
Sure! Tomorrow, Tuesday or next weekend would be best for me. Thanks!
Cool! I'm supposed to go look at a horse Saturday 1/5 at 10 but the girl has been sketchy. Any other time works, thanks!
Ok I'll see if we can do like 1pm or something
